ider-man-spinoff-movies-standalone-future/ |title=Future Spider-Man Spinoff Movies Will Stand On Their Own |last=Dumaraog |first=Ana |date=June 22, 2019 |website=[[Screen Rant]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190622224853/https://screenrant.com/spider-man-spinoff-movies-standalone-future/ |archive-date=June 22, 2019 |access-date=September 27, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Wood\">{{Cite tweet |number=1051188448667860997 |user=DiscussingFilm |title=Cinematographer Oliver Wood (\u2018The Equalizer 2\u2019, \u2018Fantastic Four\u2019) has joined the crew as cinematographer for Daniel Espinosa\u2019s \u2018MORBIUS\u2019. (Exclusive) |author=Discussing Film |date=October 14, 2018 |access-date=September 27, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190927104940/https://twitter.com/discussingfilm/status/1051188448667860997 |archive-date=September 27, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Haythe\">{{Cite web |url=https://thegww.com/exclusive-red-sparrow-scribe-justin-haythe-contributed-to-morbius-script-for-sony/ |title=Exclusive: 'Red Sparrow' Scribe Justin Haythe Contributed to 'Morbius' Script for Sony |last=Polito |first=Thomas |date=March 18, 2019 |website=Geeks WorldWide |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190927105106/https://thegww.com/exclusive-red-sparrow-scribe-justin-haythe-contributed-to-morbius-script-for-sony/ |archive-date=September 27, 2019 |access-date=September 27, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ekstrand\">{{Cite web |url=http://filmmusicreporter.com/2019/10/09/jon-ekstrand-to-score-daniel-espinosas-morbius/ |title=Jon Ekstrand to Score Daniel Espinosa\u2019s \u2018Morbius\u2019 |author=<!-- filmmusicreporter --> |date=October 9, 2019 |website=Film Music Reporter |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191010094508/http://filmmusicreporter.com/2019/10/09/jon-ekstrand-to-score-daniel-espinosas-morbius/ |archive-date=October 10, 2019 |access-date=October 10, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SonyMarve